The regular expression in MongoDB::_URI to sanitize during stringification is a bit limited.  It won't cover "mongodb+srv://" URIs and might not terminate if the path slash is missing.  Possible better would be
{noformat}
^([^:]+)://[^/?]*\@
{noformat}

